"Balance"  
  Don't Tell Me What Love Can Do  
  
  *Drop the E string to a D.*  
  *On Riff A as you pick, scrape the strings to get the scratchy effect.*  
  
  *Riff A: Pick scrape while playing notes. (Do not slide!)*  
  [E|------------------------------------------------------------|  
  B|------------------------------------------------------------|  
  G|------------------------------------------------------------|  
